    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "ac0db84a-6349-44a5-b263-5b0e36df2fbd",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showVignette",
                    "vignetteName": "FirstAidClassIndoor.png",
                    "crossFadeTime": 0
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "f47b7527-7282-4131-ba44-b037df38bc97",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f5ce399b-eb3e-4019-9b63-8e77bff0d4fd",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today's lesson will be on the Morel mushroom. This mushroom is prized by Chefs for the delicate yet distinct flavor it adds to dishes.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1fb1d7b3-2760-4442-97e6-fac78fa1c27e",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It has a narrow, honeycomb-like cap with pits and ridges on a long stem. It can be found growing on dead trees or on exposed roots in caves.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1b161eeb-cd5d-4fdb-9630-e9b99f130a3e",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It also has the magical property of temporarily enhancing a person's agility after eating it raw. This effect can be used in difficult situations which require quicker reflexes like in combat or better balance like in rock climbing.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "58ded4e9-9cac-41f7-8489-a42c1a9fac14",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Unfortunately, raw Morels have an unpleasant taste and can make you physically ill when eaten.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "41b62343-57c4-4169-a9dc-e6d253459a28",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, heroes have to take a lot of chances. Eating a Morel might improve your chances of survival in a dire situation.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "78ed7ccb-4c47-447f-bf58-d28d4e57fd53",
                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any <i>pertinent</i> questions?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "1ba0a589-d777-4fc9-abd1-54228b3e08e8",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "15f10ade-fe9c-4a69-812f-babae68ef99d",
                            "text": "Say Something Polite About Sharing Mushroom Information",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "859ea43b-8c5f-4aeb-9f51-5de659fad7a0",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "8afea9d3-3eec-4f63-bb00-0eebe67e5e1c",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d299938d-2770-41c3-950b-8c6a50b687e2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Does Chef Kinah know about these mushrooms? I'm sure she would be very interested in using them.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "01e82f2f-4777-4799-a745-cdaeca00c82f",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, it was Chef Kinah who told me about the culinary uses for the Morel. She even prepared me a dish so that I could taste them. But it was kind of you to ask, Shawn.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "8ed3e8bb-84ee-4c22-9d52-6551e2fa4314",
                            "text": "Say Something Clever About Morel Usage",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "837a34ad-a996-4dec-9c30-928a12015feb",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "73d319d8-9cf0-4a66-80d4-679afca1013e",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cfbcce72-f27a-42ed-a093-5b08a30b878e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "So cooking Morels makes them tasty but not very useful. Is there some other way to prepare the Morels that makes them edible and useful?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "62edb209-cbe0-4e5c-9411-145b65fe741b",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, and in the second session of First Aid, you can learn how to make pills that have the useful properties without the unfortunate side effects of magical mushrooms.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ec73f006-ed9d-4845-837b-b60be336d59d",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "For now though, we will deal with the fresh Morels.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "759bece3-123b-4532-ac78-c1237ca6b842",
                            "text": "Say Something Impertinent ",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "99302399-a972-4efc-8730-ee9b4fb1bc1f",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "cdf4d386-f85a-4317-9694-ab8d847aea9d",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "1e72abcb-3ca8-44ac-9874-f6711f82aea1",
                                                "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                                "amount": "1",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a3b11dda-931c-4d66-a35d-1aaf6464c1d6",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "So eating these mushrooms raw can make you sick but more agile while eating them cooked tastes good but doesn't affect your agility. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c8d76119-a09c-4572-a6cc-fd706eddaf1f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "text": "Clearly the <i>Morel</i> of this story is \"To be elite, don't heat before you eat.\"",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f41b728b-b937-4afb-b33b-a81bb7206d15",
                                    "actorId": "6b30a3a9-2324-487d-9db9-03ce174e0e80",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "<sigh>",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
